pr_title: Dhis2 10093  - New Tracker Importer GET endpoints

timeline.bodyText: I wonder if we could "merge" this interface with org.hisp.dhis.tracker.preheat.mappers.PreheatMapper. Perhaps one interface named TrackerEntityMapper. These two interfaces now are doing more or less the same thing.
